data.name: Atreides, the Distinguished
data.notes: "Atreides, the Distinguished" can be seen leaping high into the sky during the day in the northern half of Sylvalum. During the night it waits with its mouth open like a giant and highly suspicious spiked dinner plate in the sand for unsuspecting prey to move to the middle. Will call for his mate Gesserith when at low health which brings a second giant worm into the battle.
